parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The erratic transmission performance can cause the vehicle to hesitate or fail to respond when accelerating, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded in traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or fails to accelerate when taking off from a stop
the transmission does not respond at times
the vehicle makes a humming noise when trying to accelerate
the vehicle jerks or lurches when finally accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the high mount brake light can increase the risk of rear-end collisions, especially in low-visibility scenarios, as it reduces the visibility of the vehicle's braking intentions to other drivers.
symptoms: No warning lamps or messages to indicate the failure
potentially leaving the driver unaware of the issue for an extended period.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can reduce visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries, particularly in low-light conditions.
symptoms: Distorted or unclear backup camera image
failure of the backup camera to operate
